WEBVTT

02:21.558 --> 02:22.558
Hey!

02:40.327 --> 02:46.539
A girl at my door

02:50.712 --> 02:52.828
most of the income here

02:53.465 --> 03:01.338
either comes from catching octopus,
or from farming oysters and fish.

03:01.348 --> 03:07.469
Mendnets, or mend the
tools needed for fishing,

03:07.813 --> 03:09.474
that sort of thing.

03:11.608 --> 03:14.600
Uh, who do we have here?

03:15.737 --> 03:19.855
I told that woman not to ride
her bike on the main road!

03:21.618 --> 03:25.952
Mrs. jum-soon,
I told you not to ride that thing!

03:27.124 --> 03:30.457
Or at least ride it sober.
Why don't you listen?

03:30.460 --> 03:33.247
Buy me a bottle of rice wine
if you're gonna lecture me!

03:33.505 --> 03:34.620
Dammit!

03:34.631 --> 03:35.631
Who's this?

03:36.717 --> 03:38.503
Is that your new bride?

03:39.010 --> 03:40.875
Lucky you!

03:41.263 --> 03:43.879
Have fun tonight!

03:44.349 --> 03:45.885
Don't ride that thing,
it's dangerous!

03:46.017 --> 03:47.017
See ya!

04:10.792 --> 04:14.410
Damn, that was fast.

04:15.672 --> 04:18.254
He told me he was gonna pick
them up.

04:20.969 --> 04:21.969
Hey!

04:22.637 --> 04:23.626
Why so loud?

04:23.638 --> 04:24.593
You coming later?

04:24.598 --> 04:25.598
We'll see.

04:26.475 --> 04:30.764
Hey, tell your mother
to stop riding that thing!

04:30.771 --> 04:34.263
You kidding me? I'm surprised
she doesn't sleep with it.

04:34.649 --> 04:37.265
God, she's stubborn.

04:38.028 --> 04:42.397
Oh, this is our new station chief.
Say hello.

04:45.285 --> 04:46.866
She's a pretty one.

04:47.162 --> 04:48.026
Sexy girl, you know?

04:48.038 --> 04:52.532
Huh? Bastard, watch your mouth.

04:52.542 --> 04:53.542
Bye!

05:00.383 --> 05:02.499
Those guys in the car

05:03.053 --> 05:07.422
they're mostly southeast Asian
or Korean-Chinese.

05:08.058 --> 05:11.016
They're the only ones
who'll work here.

05:11.645 --> 05:13.431
It's a big problem.

05:15.065 --> 05:19.024
The only people left in this village
are senior citizens.

05:20.445 --> 05:26.566
Park yong-ha. He's the only
one in town... young man.

05:31.206 --> 05:36.200
I set out the basics for you. If you
need anything else, let me know.

05:36.211 --> 05:37.326
I'll be fine.

05:37.337 --> 05:39.703
Sorry to trouble you on
such short notice.

05:39.714 --> 05:41.170
It's no trouble!

05:41.174 --> 05:43.790
You'd be done faster if we helped.

05:43.802 --> 05:46.043
It's okay. That's everything there.

05:46.221 --> 05:48.587
They sell bottled water here, too.

05:50.308 --> 05:51.548
I'll take that.

05:51.601 --> 05:53.717
It's a bit heavy.

05:56.815 --> 06:00.728
Don't look down on us
'cause you're from Seoul.

06:00.735 --> 06:02.976
We have everything here!

06:02.988 --> 06:05.229
Except for what we don't have...

06:05.240 --> 06:06.696
Listen to you.

08:56.453 --> 09:00.787
I'm getting tired of this,
you little bitch.

09:00.790 --> 09:06.080
You act like a fucking whore.
Don't you avoid me!

09:06.087 --> 09:07.087
Hey!

09:07.589 --> 09:08.669
What are you doing there?

09:09.674 --> 09:12.086
What the fuck?

09:13.845 --> 09:16.461
This brat was supposed to give me
something, but she won't.

09:17.849 --> 09:21.683
What is it you want so badly that
you all have to gang up on her?

09:22.812 --> 09:23.847
What school do you go to?

09:23.855 --> 09:26.722
One more time, and
I'll bash your head in with this.

09:27.984 --> 09:29.349
What school?

09:30.987 --> 09:33.103
It's the middle school
down the road, right?

09:33.114 --> 09:34.229
Fuck!

09:51.841 --> 09:53.456
You go to the same
school as them?

09:57.639 --> 09:58.970
Why'd they do this to you?

10:02.852 --> 10:03.852
What's your name?

10:09.025 --> 10:12.392
It's dohee. Sun dohee.

10:14.405 --> 10:17.397
Now I know your name,
I can find them too.

10:17.909 --> 10:21.902
If they bother you again, tell them the
police will come and get them, okay?

10:35.426 --> 10:37.508
Don't be half-assed, do it in red.

10:37.512 --> 10:38.672
Here they are.

10:38.680 --> 10:40.545
They sure are.

10:40.765 --> 10:43.131
The beauty salon's going to
make some cash today.

10:43.143 --> 10:44.679
That's right!

10:44.686 --> 10:47.143
Shave their heads
nice and smooth.

10:47.147 --> 10:48.182
Hello.

10:49.691 --> 10:53.058
What do they eat that makes
them so black?

10:53.069 --> 10:56.027
Girls, hurry up
and get ready for tonight!

10:56.030 --> 10:59.693
Our chief is coming, so we
need time to prepare properly.

11:00.535 --> 11:02.526
Right, chief?

11:03.329 --> 11:04.944
Look at her laugh.

11:05.915 --> 11:08.577
I hope he doesn't get drunk
off his ass tonight.

11:08.668 --> 11:11.705
Hey, it's chief's turn now!

11:12.714 --> 11:14.830
The verse is about to start.

11:15.049 --> 11:17.335
Maybe chief wants to do
a different song.

11:17.343 --> 11:19.049
Hurry and come up here!

11:24.601 --> 11:26.592
This song's already started.

11:28.104 --> 11:34.475
She's an absolute killer

11:35.195 --> 11:40.610
I'm so attractive
and loved by many

11:42.076 --> 11:47.992
but I picked her out of the crowd

11:49.000 --> 11:54.996
you're so beautiful

11:56.007 --> 12:01.127
you're so sexy

13:21.968 --> 13:26.428
You can't throw away
bottles here.

13:28.850 --> 13:30.966
I'll clean them all up.

13:53.875 --> 13:59.245
Come over here, you little bitch!

14:55.561 --> 14:56.892
What the fuck?

14:56.896 --> 14:58.306
Are you okay?

14:58.314 --> 15:01.181
Who the fuck are you?

15:12.203 --> 15:15.161
Get away from my son!
Don't hurt him!

15:15.415 --> 15:18.452
Who the hell are you?

15:18.459 --> 15:19.949
- Leave my boy alone.
- Hey!

15:19.961 --> 15:21.076
Leave my son alone

15:21.087 --> 15:23.287
- come here and get my cell phone.
- Leave my son alone!

15:23.840 --> 15:24.670
It's in my pants pocket.

15:24.674 --> 15:31.842
Leave him alone.
You're killing him!

15:31.848 --> 15:32.963
Press 1 and hold it.

15:32.974 --> 15:35.215
You're hurting my boy.

15:35.226 --> 15:36.226
Hold it up to my ear.

15:38.354 --> 15:41.061
This is Lee young-nam.
Send a patrol car.

15:41.107 --> 15:42.813
I'm at park yong-ha's house.

15:49.365 --> 15:53.233
Hey. Wake up already.

15:53.619 --> 15:54.619
Hey!

15:56.497 --> 15:57.612
Get up.

15:58.624 --> 16:00.615
You think this is your home?

16:00.960 --> 16:02.450
Shit!

16:03.129 --> 16:04.835
What's with you?

16:05.256 --> 16:06.996
This isn't your living room.

16:07.967 --> 16:10.504
- Shit.
- Don't act like...

16:13.139 --> 16:14.504
I can't believe this.

16:14.515 --> 16:16.346
Why'd you get so drunk?

16:17.018 --> 16:19.509
You're lucky that
chief went easy on you,

16:19.520 --> 16:22.387
otherwise you'd have gone
straight to prison.

16:26.777 --> 16:28.392
Why did you beat your child?

16:29.780 --> 16:30.780
Who did?

16:32.408 --> 16:33.408
When?

16:33.659 --> 16:35.399
Don't beat your kid.

16:35.786 --> 16:39.779
Child abuse by parents is a crime. Last
night, you were caught in the act.

16:40.791 --> 16:43.874
What the fuck.

16:43.878 --> 16:48.622
I can't discipline my
own daughter?

16:48.883 --> 16:52.546
How dare you speak
to the chief that way?

16:56.766 --> 16:59.007
Go, you've been warned.

17:04.065 --> 17:07.272
- Hey.
- Get out of here.

17:07.276 --> 17:08.356
Leave.

17:11.239 --> 17:12.775
Get out.

17:16.911 --> 17:19.903
Give me a ride. You brought
me here, so take me back.

17:21.040 --> 17:22.040
Take me back.

17:24.794 --> 17:25.909
Take him.

17:33.803 --> 17:36.795
That girl isn't
yong-ha's real daughter.

17:39.267 --> 17:43.681
But he's been raising her
and sending her to school.

17:44.939 --> 17:47.555
He drinks every so often
and gets a bit deranged.

17:48.067 --> 17:51.275
But he takes care of
everything around town.

17:51.779 --> 17:55.943
This town would not run
properly without him.

17:57.076 --> 18:00.159
So we should allow him
to abuse his child?

18:01.831 --> 18:04.664
That's not what I'm saying.

18:05.084 --> 18:07.575
Alcohol is the problem.

18:40.494 --> 18:41.609
Sun dohee!

18:44.081 --> 18:45.081
Come over here.

18:54.216 --> 18:57.583
How often does your father
hit you like that?

19:10.024 --> 19:12.265
Are you mute?
Why don't you talk?

19:16.906 --> 19:18.988
You can't let him beat you
that way.

19:21.035 --> 19:23.276
He doesn't hit me
when he doesn't drink.

19:30.795 --> 19:33.286
- Dohee.
- Yes?

19:35.383 --> 19:39.752
When an adult hits a child,
it's a very bad thing.

19:41.055 --> 19:47.142
If someone beats you that hard,
you need to tell someone, okay?

19:59.281 --> 20:00.281
Miss...

20:01.951 --> 20:04.192
Is it okay if I try the hat on?

20:16.966 --> 20:17.966
Salute!

20:19.051 --> 20:21.963
If you're gonna do it,
do it right. Like this.

20:33.607 --> 20:37.475
You fucking little bitch! How
dare you stand there blabbering?

20:37.486 --> 20:39.317
Come here, you filthy mutt.

20:43.951 --> 20:45.612
Damn bitch.

20:46.996 --> 20:48.361
Stop right there!

20:57.214 --> 21:02.959
You no good fucking bitch,
got no respect.

21:02.970 --> 21:05.006
Stop babbling, you fucker!

21:05.014 --> 21:07.630
Bitch!

21:08.726 --> 21:10.262
You dirty little bitch.

21:45.930 --> 21:49.297
Did you know the alumni association
was called because of you?

21:51.185 --> 21:55.554
Investigations have been started,
a lot of people are in hot water.

21:57.441 --> 21:58.521
I'm sorry.

21:59.068 --> 22:02.902
This won't end just because
you say sorry and get relocated.

22:04.949 --> 22:09.192
Anyway, watch yourself
in shallower waters.

22:10.079 --> 22:12.912
It's easier to be scrutinized
in a small town.

22:13.207 --> 22:16.040
Word travels fast, got it?

22:16.043 --> 22:20.036
Happens again, no one can look after you.
Be careful.

22:27.346 --> 22:28.586
Get your act together.

22:32.726 --> 22:34.006
Inspector Lee young-nam is here.

22:35.229 --> 22:36.560
Lee young-nam, sir.

22:40.568 --> 22:41.568
Sit down.

22:52.997 --> 22:55.238
With your help,
I was safely reassigned.

22:55.249 --> 22:58.741
Sure. It's been 10 days?

22:58.752 --> 23:00.458
Yes, sir.

23:09.138 --> 23:14.633
I don't have any bias in that area.

23:14.643 --> 23:18.386
I don't want to make a fuss over
someone's personal affair.

23:19.899 --> 23:22.015
But we are part of a community.

23:23.652 --> 23:27.236
We shouldn't do things
that we know will cause trouble.

23:30.242 --> 23:31.882
We have the school's
reputation to uphold.

23:35.164 --> 23:39.407
If you lay low for about a year,
you should be able to return.

23:44.298 --> 23:45.788
Thank you.

23:47.509 --> 23:48.509
All right.

23:50.262 --> 23:53.004
Take good care of yourself.
Thank you.

25:16.015 --> 25:19.007
Chief Lee, come here
and have a drink with us!

25:19.018 --> 25:22.886
Come on, we're roasting fish here!

25:23.022 --> 25:26.014
It's windy today. Come and play!

25:26.734 --> 25:30.397
Dohee, come here!

25:30.654 --> 25:32.235
Hey!

25:32.239 --> 25:40.239
What're you doing out
in the middle of the night?

25:40.914 --> 25:44.031
Hey, when your father
talks to you...

25:44.418 --> 25:45.749
That little shit.

25:47.296 --> 25:49.252
Huh? Isn't that the chief?

25:50.299 --> 25:55.669
She's been following
the chief around lately.

25:55.679 --> 25:57.920
She's clingy, like her mother.

26:30.047 --> 26:31.787
Why do you keep following me?

26:31.965 --> 26:33.330
You got something to say?

26:38.222 --> 26:39.428
Then what's wrong?

26:46.605 --> 26:47.605
Get on.

26:55.239 --> 26:57.981
Hold on tight,
I'm going to go really fast.

27:18.887 --> 27:21.629
What were you doing there
this morning?

27:27.104 --> 27:29.641
I thought you were gonna
drown yourself in the sea.

27:31.358 --> 27:32.768
I was practicing dance.

28:23.202 --> 28:27.946
Go home. Don't roam around
at night. It's dangerous.

28:32.461 --> 28:33.701
What's wrong?

28:42.721 --> 28:46.805
Can I go with you?

28:59.112 --> 29:00.352
Get inside.

29:13.210 --> 29:16.998
You fucking bitch.
Where the fuck were you?

29:17.005 --> 29:23.592
Stupid mutt. Acting like
a mutt, just like her mom.

29:38.151 --> 29:41.018
Eun-jung

30:27.200 --> 30:28.565
What happened?

30:44.718 --> 30:45.718
Yes?

30:47.095 --> 30:48.175
What?

30:50.682 --> 30:53.845
The body of an old woman?
A motorcycle?

30:56.355 --> 30:57.720
I'll be right there.

31:03.570 --> 31:05.982
I was called to the scene
at 04:40 hours.

31:06.365 --> 31:10.358
I'll need a crime scene investigator.
Please alert the fire department.

31:11.745 --> 31:12.985
It's a death.

31:14.373 --> 31:16.079
It looks like an accidental death.

31:19.127 --> 31:20.742
First, find park yong-ha.

31:21.755 --> 31:22.755
Yes, ma'am.

31:35.018 --> 31:37.475
Do you know what happened?

31:38.647 --> 31:40.888
What did you see?

31:41.608 --> 31:45.897
Dad chased me.

31:46.905 --> 31:49.521
Dad beat me so I ran away.

31:49.658 --> 31:51.398
And grandma chased me.

31:52.244 --> 31:55.611
Then she fell into the sea.

31:56.665 --> 31:59.372
I ran away to avoid
getting beat up.

32:00.419 --> 32:03.252
You saw her fall in the sea?

32:04.297 --> 32:07.255
Dad beat me.

32:08.051 --> 32:11.293
So I ran, and grandma chased me.

32:12.639 --> 32:13.924
Said she'll kill me.

32:18.812 --> 32:22.430
Were you here with your grandma?

32:25.318 --> 32:26.774
Did you...

32:28.530 --> 32:29.940
Did you do something?

32:35.787 --> 32:41.953
Dad beat me.
I ran so not to get hit.

32:43.712 --> 32:46.044
You told me not to
let him beat me.

32:46.840 --> 32:54.840
But when grandma got on the bike
to get me, she fell in the sea.

32:57.601 --> 33:04.973
I was so scared of the sea.

33:09.362 --> 33:11.978
Okay. It's all right.

33:14.117 --> 33:15.232
It's yong-ha.

33:19.122 --> 33:20.122
What took you so long?

33:26.630 --> 33:28.746
Mom.

33:30.383 --> 33:37.004
Mom.

33:37.015 --> 33:38.630
Dammit.

33:42.145 --> 33:43.510
You fucking bitch!

33:45.232 --> 33:48.895
That bitch attacked me yesterday.
She had wild eyes!

33:48.902 --> 33:51.268
I heard you left home,
and your mother too.

33:51.530 --> 33:54.272
The girl came to my house
after her father beat her.

33:56.618 --> 34:00.531
Why blame the girl
when you were out drinking?

34:00.539 --> 34:03.656
I saw her acting up before I left!

34:03.667 --> 34:08.036
She ran to the chief scared for
her life, after you beat her.

34:08.045 --> 34:09.911
You're not making sense!

34:10.590 --> 34:13.831
From what I see,
alcohol is the problem.

34:15.303 --> 34:19.342
What shall we do?
Take her to the morgue?

34:19.349 --> 34:22.716
We don't know how she died.

34:22.726 --> 34:24.934
We need... what you call it!

34:24.938 --> 34:27.554
Autopsy. We need an autopsy.

34:27.565 --> 34:30.353
Do you even know what
an autopsy is?

34:30.360 --> 34:33.978
They cut her open,
and take out all of her organs.

34:33.989 --> 34:36.605
Do it!

34:36.616 --> 34:38.231
Damn.

34:38.243 --> 34:40.234
Everyone, clear out now.

34:41.246 --> 34:46.081
- Mom!
- Everyone go home.

34:46.585 --> 34:52.376
She was heavily intoxicated with a
blood alcohol content of 0.2%.

34:52.382 --> 34:57.126
And she was in the early stages
of Alzheimer's disease.

34:58.471 --> 35:02.885
We believe she shouldn't
have been operating a vehicle.

35:03.893 --> 35:09.980
We find the cause of death
to be drowning

35:09.983 --> 35:12.895
as a result of careless driving.

35:22.287 --> 35:25.495
Sign here with your thumbprint.

35:36.301 --> 35:37.666
Does the girl need to sign too?

35:41.181 --> 35:44.673
Come over here, sweetie.

35:48.438 --> 35:49.518
Wipe your thumb.

35:52.317 --> 35:54.399
You sign here too.

35:59.824 --> 36:00.904
Go sit over there.

36:07.040 --> 36:08.480
What do you want to do
with the bike?

36:09.584 --> 36:10.664
I'll take it.

36:11.461 --> 36:14.077
It's useless now
that it fell in the sea.

36:14.089 --> 36:15.454
Don't touch it!

37:03.596 --> 37:05.712
This isn't working.
Come with me.

37:28.163 --> 37:30.370
That son of a bitch.

37:33.042 --> 37:34.042
Can we...

37:35.420 --> 37:37.536
Just stay here?

37:46.514 --> 37:49.551
Okay, first take a hot shower.

38:09.204 --> 38:11.069
When is your mom coming?

38:12.081 --> 38:13.821
Why did she leave you here?

38:15.335 --> 38:17.326
She won't come back this time.

38:20.048 --> 38:22.084
I knew it the day she left.

38:23.468 --> 38:25.959
I saw her leave with her luggage
in the middle of the night.

38:27.722 --> 38:32.967
I made eye contact with her, but
she told me to go back to sleep.

38:34.562 --> 38:40.228
Until then, she'd tell me to get
dressed when I asked to come along.

38:49.744 --> 38:55.114
Do you think you get beaten
because of your mother?

38:57.377 --> 38:59.493
My own mother abandoned me.

39:06.511 --> 39:08.126
Do you want to stay here
for a while?

39:09.264 --> 39:12.631
Really?
Can I really stay with you?

39:13.017 --> 39:15.599
Get some sleep for now.

39:25.280 --> 39:27.020
What about you?

39:27.657 --> 39:29.488
I'll sleep in the living room.

39:30.285 --> 39:31.365
Why?

39:32.370 --> 39:34.031
I like sleeping alone.

39:35.415 --> 39:36.530
Okay.

40:18.833 --> 40:22.451
What're you doing?

40:23.463 --> 40:26.045
Chief, I'm hungry.

40:26.299 --> 40:27.584
Okay.

41:20.853 --> 41:22.263
I want to wear this too.

41:24.148 --> 41:26.855
Even the smallest size would be
too big for you.

41:27.110 --> 41:30.102
- This one's pretty too.
- I don't like it.

41:48.506 --> 41:49.916
This is awesome.

41:57.140 --> 41:58.425
Take out your cell phone.

42:04.439 --> 42:06.145
Hold down number 1.

42:11.404 --> 42:13.315
Number 2 is the police station.

42:13.322 --> 42:15.313
If I don't pick up,
call the station.

42:16.284 --> 42:21.699
If your dad tries to hit you again,
run and call me, okay?

42:27.420 --> 42:28.785
Okay.

42:38.598 --> 42:39.963
Look!

43:03.498 --> 43:04.738
Good job.

43:05.625 --> 43:07.707
Now come and eat.

43:13.508 --> 43:16.124
Where did you learn
to sing and dance?

43:16.135 --> 43:19.753
I just picked it up while watching TV.
I'm great at imitating.

43:20.348 --> 43:22.009
What else can you do?

43:23.893 --> 43:27.135
Once upon a time,

43:27.146 --> 43:30.013
there lived a little mermaid.

43:30.274 --> 43:36.520
Under water, she had fins for
legs and a pretty torso.

43:37.031 --> 43:39.022
Her body truly had a twist ending.

43:39.784 --> 43:43.652
The fast dolphin is sleek.

43:46.874 --> 43:49.160
I'll rip you to pieces!

43:49.293 --> 43:54.253
Nice. You sound exactly the same
let's eat.

43:59.428 --> 44:01.510
How's the food?

44:23.202 --> 44:24.658
Excuse me.

44:24.704 --> 44:30.449
A day has passed, and my kid
doesn't even think of coming home.

44:30.459 --> 44:35.579
The people in town said
she'd be here.

44:35.590 --> 44:39.048
I know it's late, but I had to come.

44:39.051 --> 44:42.339
Hi baby, you were here?

44:43.055 --> 44:46.547
Can't you even say
hello to your father, bitch?

44:49.604 --> 44:51.344
Why do you hit your child?

44:51.856 --> 44:55.064
Who? Who hit his child?

44:55.943 --> 44:57.604
