01:15:11.507 --> 01:15:12.622
Hey.

01:15:34.739 --> 01:15:35.899
What's wrong with you?

01:15:36.490 --> 01:15:38.026
Are you gonna go to that woman?

01:15:38.659 --> 01:15:41.025
