01:16:17.573 --> 01:16:18.813
What are you talking about?

01:16:18.824 --> 01:16:23.158
Did I startle you?
You thought no one knew?

01:16:24.455 --> 01:16:27.572
You take all the sweetness
of a little girl.

01:16:27.583 --> 01:16:30.450
