Why are you arresting me?

01:18:59.860 --> 01:19:00.940
Let's go.

01:19:00.945 --> 01:19:02.731
Call my boss. Call Mr. choi.

01:19:02.738 --> 01:19:04.603
We went to escort him too.

01:19:04.865 --> 01:19:05.945
Fuck.

01:19:05.950 --> 01:19:08.066
